The game "La methode de Claude" is an educational game created by the doctor Janek Hyzewicz. Dr. Janek Hyzewicz is an assistant teacher of the departement of life sciences of UNIVERSITE D'EVRY VAL D'ESSONNE, also known as Universit√© Evry-Paris Saclay (official site: https://www.univ-evry.fr/accueil.html).

The data your app stores, and which of these is "personally identifiable information"?
Data stores login and password of the users. We do not collect these informations, they are stored directly in the phone.
    
The data your app transmits to your servers.
No data are collected: we do not have servers for data collection.

How the above data is used.
Data are only used to keep in memory the progression of individual players.

Whether it is possible to request deletion of this data.
User can delete data in their phones.

The permissions that your app use, especially if you use any sensitive permissions like READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.
App do not use specific permission.

How you want to be contacted in case someone wishes to ask for clarification/deletion of data/report security vulnerability.
You can contact me for any clarification at janek.hyzewicz@univ-evry.fr
